Product name: MTG CUSTOM PROXY
Description:
I am making proxy/alternate art cards for Magic the Gathering. These fine detailed pieces of art will definitely set your opponent off balance when playing. Or show them off as a desk piece or art piece for just general viewing. I can/will make any card that has been released in the MTG universe as an alternate art card. Doing this should allow for use in most tournaments. I would also be happy to make proxy cards of characters with custom cost, abilities, colors, etc.... These cards will be 63mm x 88mm in size and will be just like a regular magic card and will be shipped in  standard Ultra Pro Top Loaders. I am also currently looking into doing holo cards (update coming soon).
Feel free to email me your custom artwork to put on these cards, or just give me an idea of what you are looking for and I will be happy to make them to order.
If you decide to send me art work to use I do require the original artist/s to be cited so they can be credited for the work they have put into making that art. 
I will be adding more pictures as I go for reference of my products.
Legal:
I DO NOT own the rights to the artwork used (unless cited as myself) and am not in anyway affiliated with Wizards of the Coast. These are fan made art concepts.
